quran[10{c,v,t}:
6,9,aur agar hum farishtay ko utaartay tab bhi usay insani shakal hi mein utaartay aur is terhan inhen usi shuba mein mubtala kar dete jis mein ab yeh mubtala hain
6,10,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum se pehlay bhi bohat se Rasolo-n ka mazaq uraya ja chuka hai, magar un mazaq urane walon par aakhir-kaar wohi haqeeqat musallat ho kar rahi jis ka woh mazaq uratay thay"
6,11,"inn se kaho, zara zameen mein chal phir kar dekho jhutlanay walon ka kya injaam howa hai"
6,12,"un se pucho, asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai woh kis kaahe? kaho sab kuch Allah hi ka hai, is ne reham o karam ka Shewa apne oopar lazim kar liya hai ( isi liye woh nafarmanio-n aursarkasyun اpar tumhe jaldi se nahi pakar laita ), qayamat ke roz woh tum sab ko zaroor jama kere ga, yeh bilkul aik ghair mushtaba haqeeqat hai, magar jin logon ne apne aap ko khud tabahi ke khatray mein mubtala kar liya hai woh usay nahi mantay"
6,13,"raat ke andheray aur din ke ujalay mein jo kuchtehra howa hai, sab Allah ka hai aur woh sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
6,14,"kaho, Allah ko chore kar kya mein kisi aur ko apna sir parast bana lon? uss khuda ko chore kar jo zameen o aasman ka khaaliq hai aur jo rozi deta hai rozi laita nahi hai? kaho, mujhe to yahi hukum diya gaya hai ke sab se pehlay mein uss ke agay sir tasleem khham karoon ( aur takeed ki gayi hai ke koi shirk karta hai to kere ) to behar haal mushrikon mein shaamil nah ho"
6,15,"kaho, agar mein apne rab ki nafarmani karoon to darta hon ke aik barray ( khofnaak ) din mujhe saza bhgtni parre gi"
6,16,uss din jo saza se bach gaya is par Allah ne bara hi reham kya aur yahi numaya kamyabi hai
6,17,"agar Allah tumhe kisi qisam ka nuqsaan p_hnchaye to is ke siwa koi nahi jo tumhe is nuqsaan se bacha sakay, aur agar woh tumhe kisi bhalai se behra mand kere to woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
6,18,woh apne bundon par kaamil ikhtiyarat rakhta hai aur Dana aur bakhabar hai
